title.narrative: ADAP(01) MTR TECHNICAL LEADERSHIP ON ADOLESCENTS DEVELOPMENT & PARTICIPATION

description.narrative: Technical leadership on adolescents development and participation Countries have technical capacity to scale up interventions to deliver results across sectors for adolescent development and participation, which contributes to Adolescent Empowerment. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Every Child an Equitable Chance in Life By 2021, UNICEF supported countries apply relevant policies, innovative approaches and evidence, to design and implement publicly and privately funded development and humanitarian interventions at scale, that give Every Child an Equitable Chance in Life
